(CONTINUADO)
HARRY
S´en lo. *
A Hermione n-xi t-xo´n twi´ extzen a Harry n-chi tzaj t-xnaq´tza´n twitz, ximana ti´j Ron exttzen *
Ginny. Ik tzeʼn in nel tnikʼ tiʼj twitz, in meltzʼaj Ron ex in che *
q´onxa jun twitz, jun ti´x mya tzaj q´ama´n extzun ax tok n-ik´x *
kyxol. *
Tojx ambʼil aju, in jatz jun bʼitz toj kyaʼj, in tzaj bʼaj tkʼuʼj ex in tzaj xobʼ xjal tuʼn, *
extzen junjun segundos t-xe´l jun PICH´ n-el t-xo´n tib´aj t-xe´ *
aju torreta mas matij ex in xi tzyet tuʼn t-xi t-xbʼalumin tibʼ toj *
kya´j. *
A Ron exttzen a Ginny n-chi b´et ky-txlaj Harry exttzen Hermione, n-chi ky-okx ky-q´ob´ twitz *
aju t-xlekumal. Kykyaqil in che keʼyin twitz kyaʼj, in che keʼyin tiʼj chyuʼj *
ch´iy ch´in t-xilen extzen t-b´itz -- magia -- n-chi b´et. *
Mix a’lx jun q’mante jun yol. *
FADE OUT.
A B´ajsb´il
